public class NewtonJointRecord extends Object
NewtonJointRecord relies on preview features of the Java platform:
  • NewtonJointRecord refers to one or more preview APIs: MemoryLayout, MemorySegment, SegmentAllocator, SegmentScope.
Programs can only use NewtonJointRecord when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
